The system will manage employees, licenses, training compliance, scheduling, incidents, onboarding, and overall HR workflows.

You may choose the most efficient and modern tech stack, but the frontend UI must use ShadCN or a similar modern component library.

Build clean, scalable, maintainable code following best practices.

